.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-g \&, \ \-\-global
Install packages globally.
.TP
.BI \-\-registry \ URL
Use the specified npm registry URL.
.TP
.BI \-\-prefix \ PATH
The prefix to install packages to.
.TP
.BI \-v \&, \ \-\-version
Print npm version.
.TP
.BI \-h \&, \ \-\-help
Print npm help.
.TP
.BI \-f \&, \ \-\-force
Force installation.
.TP
.BI \-\-save
Save installed packages to dependencies.
.TP
.BI \-\-save-dev
Save installed packages to devDependencies.

